N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 152.13 - Application for extension of time

State Regulations

All applications for extensions of time must be
delivered, mailed, or transmitted to the address or location as directed in the
appropriate forms and instructions (see Part 157 of this

Article). Notes
